<title>kl ywm tḥt ṣlybk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- kl ywm tḥt ṣlybk .. knt bạfkr dạymaⁿạ fyk yạ rby wạ̉jy lk
 mn gẖyr kẖwf zy ạ̉bwyạ .. ʿn ạ̉srạry wʿn ḥkạyạty hnạk bạḥkylk
 knt ktyr yạ rby bạfkr .. mn dlwqty wḥty̱ ạ̉mạ ạ̉kbr
 ạ̹ny lạ ymkn ywm hạtgẖyr .. wạ̉nsy̱ ṣlybk
 knt fy qlby dạymaⁿạ ạ̉ṣly .. yfḍl ḥbk fyã tmly
 wmạfysẖ ḥạjẗ fy ywm tmnʿny ... ạ̹ny ậjy lk wạfḍl ạ̉ḥky lk
 2- wạ̉mạ kbr nạdytk tạny .. bs lqyt fy ạ̹ydyã yạ rby qywd mạnʿạny
 ḥzn wkẖwf mạly kyạny .. sjn kẖṭyẗ wḥb wsẖhwẗ ʿạlm fạny
 wbqyt tạny yạ rb bạfkr .. ạ̹mty̱ ạ̉rjʿ lk wạ̹zạy hạqdr
 ạ̉qʿd zy mạ knt ṣgẖyr .. tḥt ṣlybk
 wbqyt tạny fy qlby bạṣly .. ạ̹nk tgẖfr ly wtkẖly
 sẖhwẗ qlby wrwḥy tmly .. ạ̹ny ậjy lk wạfḍl ạ̉ḥky lk
 3- wạ̉mạ rjʿt lqytk ḥạny .. byn ạ̉ḥḍạn ạlậb fy ạlrwḥ frḥ ymlạny
 msḥt dmwʿy jddt kyạny .. bạʿtrạfạt mn ʿmq ạlqlb ndm jwạny
 wạ̹zạy bqy̱ yạ rb hạkạfỷk .. ʿly̱ gẖfrạnk wʿly̱ rʿạytk
 hạfḍl ṭwl ạlwqt ạ̉ṭạwʿk .. jwh ṭryqk
 wykwn qlby byrnm lk .. ṭwl ạlʿmr hạmjd ạsmk
 ạ̉gẖly̱ mạ ʿndh byqdm lk lmạ ậjy lk wạfḍl ạ̉ḥky lk</lyrics>
</song>